window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"Retribution proves that the scariest story is the true story. Here's the real intelligence operation.\" —Brad Meltzer</p><p>A shattering debut thriller in which an unstoppable force of destruction is about to strike at the heart of America.</p><p>The remote and impenetrable Pakistani mountains have offered refuge to the worst enemies of civilization since the time of Alexander. Now, the world faces a new challenge. Reared from birth to harbor a seething hatred, a lone man is about to unleash a firestorm that will rage for centuries. And the window of opportunity to stop him is shutting much faster than Washington D.C. can hope to deal with.</p><p>A top lethal operative, Will Parker is embedded within the terrorist's ranks to stop this catastrophic disaster. But with a nuclear core on its way to the U.S., Parker will go to any lengths to stop a biological terror more lethal than anything the USA—and the world—has ever faced.</p><p>Retribution—a dire warning of what our future may hold…and our end.</p>"; 
